Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.90,0:06:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝各位的聆聽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.90,0:06:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 好歹說點感想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.65,0:06:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 挺好的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.85,0:06:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠被友利同學誇獎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.28,0:06:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚咲林好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.66,0:06:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 你剛才自稱柚咲林所以要扣分
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.98,0:07:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在友利同學心目中 現在究竟得了幾分呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.37,0:07:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌10分 曲20分 服裝20分 編輯30分
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.82,0:07:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而由於本人犯病要扣51分
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.72,0:07:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.76,0:07:13.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.18,0:07:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,29分
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.64,0:07:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？這不是不及格嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.13,0:07:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請單獨為PV重新打分
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.68,0:07:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就80分
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.76,0:07:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.86,0:07:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了 柚咲林好高興
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.34,0:07:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下降到19分了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.99,0:07:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣柚咲同學不是變得像笨蛋一樣了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.61,0:07:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 我又不是你的什麼死忠歌迷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.22,0:07:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從生意角度上來講我認為是100分滿分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.72,0:07:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 以你來說真是出乎意料..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.85,0:07:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了 好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.70,0:07:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了呢 柚咲林
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.59,0:07:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚咲林 LUCKY~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.72,0:07:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之我想再看一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.81,0:07:49.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？這次是最後一遍哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.02,0:07:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 真慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.99,0:07:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 今天那傢夥不會來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.22,0:08:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？那麼為什麼召集我們？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.55,0:08:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 這個嘛..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.15,0:08:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鏘
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.71,0:08:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個..這是“ZHIEND”的演唱會門票
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.62,0:08:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且這是明天的票啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.78,0:08:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZHIEND？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.24,0:08:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚咲同學你不知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.41,0:08:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是友利同學最喜歡的搖滾樂隊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.80,0:08:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是搖滾 是後搖滾啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.56,0:08:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後搖滾？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.45,0:08:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去維基查查吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.58,0:08:26.72,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}文化的起源 1980年代
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.58,0:08:26.72,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}使用樂器 吉他 貝斯 大鼓 大提琴 聲樂 木管樂器等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.58,0:08:26.72,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}流行時代 從發祥至現在一直保持不錯的評價
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.58,0:08:26.72,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}後搖滾是搖滾的一種 從旋律·和音·音色·和弦等方面上來說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.58,0:08:26.72,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}具有原來的搖滾中看不到的特徵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.10,0:08:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越來越糊塗了..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.99,0:08:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事無所謂啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.58,0:08:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡有兩張“ZHIEND”的演唱會門票
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.91,0:08:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 該怎麼處理它們就是問題所在了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.25,0:08:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有點聽不懂耶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.65,0:08:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 她還可以帶一個人去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.01,0:08:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.84,0:08:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我對那個什麼什麼搖滾不太熟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.21,0:08:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在海外的評價和知名度非常高的說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.12,0:08:55.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果說你的歌是100分滿分的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.51,0:08:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼“ZHIEND”就是一百萬分
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.55,0:08:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然還有滿分以上的分數啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.11,0:09:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 沒有人主動報名麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.17,0:09:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒有太大的興趣呢..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.68,0:09:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以乙坂同學 你意下如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.71,0:09:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？我？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.91,0:09:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好呢 和友利同學兩個人一起去如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.74,0:09:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 這種消除法一樣的決定方式是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.27,0:09:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美砂呢？我們還沒有征求美砂的意見呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.01,0:09:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能聽到BPM260的超高速雙底鼓我就去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.01,0:09:23.33,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}BPM：Beat Per Minute，每分鐘節拍數的單位。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.71,0:09:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不能聽到BPM260的超高速雙底鼓所以算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.46,0:09:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 就決定是乙坂同學了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.69,0:09:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.09,0:09:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾一次也挺好的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.76,0:09:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息放鬆也是必要的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.84,0:09:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了 那就我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.28,0:09:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.65,0:09:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.83,0:09:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她眼睛看不見嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.05,0:10:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼避開我？該死
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.05,0:10:02.33,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why avoid me?shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.10,0:10:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那是什麼..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.09,0:10:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難不成..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.17,0:10:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個..How..怎麼說來著？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.51,0:10:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會請我吃摩登燒嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.51,0:10:19.61,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}摩登燒：加入燒麵的關西風御喜燒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.87,0:10:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？你會說日語嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.48,0:10:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是摩登燒啦 摩·登·燒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.92,0:10:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩登燒？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.45,0:10:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是麼..沒有人知道 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.47,0:10:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是日本 為什麼..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.47,0:10:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上帝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.17,0:10:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是指加麵的御喜燒嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.32,0:10:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 正是如此 麵條！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.28,0:10:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪裡能吃到？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.55,0:10:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果廣島燒也行的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.12,0:10:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那普通的御喜燒店應該都有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.19,0:10:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡頭有加麵條嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.09,0:10:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.27,0:10:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請務必帶我去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.63,0:10:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了 明白了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.84,0:10:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.40,0:10:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廣島燒一份
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.70,0:10:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有中杯生啤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.82,0:10:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.61,0:11:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我要烏龍茶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.59,0:11:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.16,0:11:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不 廣島燒點兩份好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.54,0:11:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.39,0:11:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家也不會有人幫我準備好晚餐了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.94,0:11:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得快點習慣這種生活
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.86,0:11:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 真爽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.57,0:11:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們自己煎嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.97,0:11:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不 這個人眼睛看不見
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.43,0:11:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請幫我們做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.35,0:11:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.46,0:11:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？眼睛看不見是指..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.40,0:11:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 難不成..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.26,0:11:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好你好 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.51,0:11:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是“ZHIEND”的主唱莎拉·夏恩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.32,0:11:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.82,0:11:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎..莎拉小姐居然大駕光臨我這簡陋的御喜燒店
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.58,0:11:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 明天的演唱會我會去的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.29,0:11:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所所所以呢 請幫我在紙箋上簽名
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.85,0:11:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.86,0:11:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛看不見也寫得很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.41,0:11:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.00,0:11:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.68,0:12:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼這道菜請您享用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.56,0:12:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼問題嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.48,0:12:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麵漿好稀！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.71,0:12:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 畢竟不是摩登燒 味道當然有差異啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.34,0:12:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 不過很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.14,0:12:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是日本
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.91,0:12:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝兩位的惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.47,0:12:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很期待您的演唱會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.83,0:12:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 讓你招待了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.66,0:12:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.27,0:12:33.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是遇到了什麼不好的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.99,0:12:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過氣息和聲色就能明白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.10,0:12:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直散發著濃濃的悲壯感呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.63,0:12:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是因為..那個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.64,0:12:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去了親近的人 之類的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.29,0:12:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害啊 正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.15,0:12:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你願意的話 能否說來聽聽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.96,0:13:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在前一陣子 妹妹因為事故去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.25,0:13:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然是這樣..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.34,0:13:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對我這麼熱心腸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.43,0:13:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為表謝意至少讓我為你妹妹獻煙吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.08,0:13:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獻煙？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.39,0:13:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指上香嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.44,0:13:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.54,0:13:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不 你不需要那麼..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.95,0:13:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 請讓我去上香吧 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.90,0:13:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了 明白了啦 請你把頭抬起來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.26,0:13:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個..我有一個請求
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.02,0:13:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想請你去見一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.03,0:13:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一對兄妹很喜歡你的樂隊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.41,0:13:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來他們不是普通的歌迷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.66,0:13:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的沒錯 請等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.20,0:13:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔細一想 我還從沒給她打過電話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.74,0:13:58.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我是友利
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.92,0:14:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那個..我是乙坂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.32,0:14:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 是你啊 真少見呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.24,0:14:05.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問有什麼事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.04,0:14:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了 你可別太吃驚哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.85,0:14:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我正和“ZHIEND”的主唱在一塊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.19,0:14:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.11,0:14:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？你不吃驚嗎？難不成不信我？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.05,0:14:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我相信 畢竟說這種謊話對你沒好處啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.97,0:14:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 你有何貴幹？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.04,0:14:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能和她見面哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.17,0:14:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？見她做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.19,0:14:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼..你可以跟她聊天啊 事實上我也..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.24,0:14:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算能見面我也不會特地去見的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.08,0:14:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是喜歡“ZHIEND”的歌和演奏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.94,0:14:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要聽他們的CD和演唱會 僅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.33,0:14:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒誒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.81,0:14:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你找我就是為了這事麼？我掛了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.82,0:14:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不 不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.50,0:14:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有話快說啊 還有什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.41,0:14:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你久等了 那個人的所在之處離這裡有點遠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.99,0:14:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問你必須幾點回去？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.80,0:14:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間什麼的無所謂啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.16,0:15:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 你要帶我上哪都行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.11,0:15:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今 你的大事就等於是我的大事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.35,0:15:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是明天就是演唱會了 真的沒問題嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.34,0:15:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樂隊成員和製作人會幫我打點好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.69,0:15:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 幫大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.56,0:15:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須打個電話說不回去吃了..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.78,0:15:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 又來了 她已經不在了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.09,0:15:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又唉聲嘆氣了 難不成想起妹妹了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.67,0:15:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是什麼事都被你看穿了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.51,0:15:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子餓了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.93,0:15:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？不是剛剛才吃過嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.38,0:15:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才是午餐 現在是晚餐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.10,0:15:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想吃什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.18,0:15:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到電車 就是立食蕎麥麵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.35,0:16:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太令人吃驚了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.90,0:16:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可樂餅蕎麥麵這道菜品
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.05,0:16:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在是太美妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.20,0:16:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇跡般的化學反應
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.23,0:16:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想出這道菜的人值得尊敬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.18,0:16:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.22,0:16:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我可以問你個問題嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.64,0:16:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然可以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.47,0:16:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思這問題可能有些敏感 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.53,0:16:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的眼睛..是完全看不到嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.43,0:16:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 什麼都看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.13,0:16:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你能簽名 說明不是天生就看不見吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.61,0:16:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 但是這是懺悔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.75,0:16:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懺悔？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.93,0:16:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可以說是贖罪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.20,0:16:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有考慮過人生嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.15,0:16:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼突然提起這個了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.23,0:16:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂人生啊 過去就無法重來對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.63,0:16:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那當然
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.66,0:16:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直夢想著能成為樂隊主唱站在舞臺之上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.77,0:17:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我的人生 在我醒悟之時就為時已晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.05,0:17:05.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒能實現那個夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.24,0:17:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無論唱歌還是彈吉他都很差勁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.70,0:17:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在電視上看到那些年紀相近的歌手廣受讚譽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.45,0:17:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對神產生了憎恨..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.07,0:17:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你現在已經夢想實現了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.93,0:17:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為我作弊了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.22,0:17:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作弊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.49,0:17:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且單純是為了自己的慾望
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.49,0:17:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾經也在日本大賣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.54,0:17:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獲得了種種成功 成為了社會現象 話題人物 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.60,0:17:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龐大的資金在運作 身邊的眼光也變了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.34,0:17:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是朝壞的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.65,0:17:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果還把家人牽扯了進來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.41,0:17:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時還有人為了錢綁架過我的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.40,0:17:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我罷手不幹了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.34,0:17:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到頭來 我決心做一個不起眼的樂隊主唱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.02,0:17:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後 作為交換我獻出了視力 The·End
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.40,0:17:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獻給了誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.32,0:18:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是神明大人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.36,0:18:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨 現在的你當然不會懂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.06,0:18:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 如果有朝一日你也經歷到這一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.15,0:18:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定要好好幹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.18,0:18:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然目的地已經能看到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.27,0:18:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是還需要再走一會
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.63,0:18:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.38,0:18:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 把你帶來這麼遠的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.21,0:18:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 你自己發覺了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.41,0:18:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的你很溫柔哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.59,0:18:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以前不是這樣的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.77,0:18:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我自己沒發覺 不過真是如此吧..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.09,0:18:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定遇到了不錯的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.29,0:18:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是的話 這個人只會是友利了..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.34,0:18:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那傢夥讓我..？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.30,0:18:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有話快說啊 還有什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.73,0:18:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想讓這個人和你哥哥見面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.62,0:18:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.87,0:19:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的哥哥很早以前就是“ZHIEND”的歌迷了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.59,0:19:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.44,0:19:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和這個樂隊的主唱見面的話 說不定會發生些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.19,0:19:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的意思是會發生什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.91,0:19:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如說 清醒過來之類的..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.51,0:19:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能有這麼好的事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.00,0:19:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我想賭一把
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.66,0:19:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這倒也並非完全沒可能 那就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.30,0:19:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.54,0:19:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你為什麼要幫我哥哥做到這個地步？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.71,0:19:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 那是因為..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.66,0:19:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實如此 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.22,0:19:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這種人 反而只會禍害他人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.59,0:19:36.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.11,0:19:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是..一時興起而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.68,0:19:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這個嘛 怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.47,0:19:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.95,0:19:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼能請你通知醫院說我和莎拉會去探訪嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.07,0:19:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.11,0:19:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道他現在是什麼狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.90,0:19:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你做好心理準備
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.81,0:20:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 透過你的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.88,0:20:03.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉重的感覺已經完全傳達給我了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.72,0:20:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鎮靜劑又用完了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.76,0:20:13.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常奇妙的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.62,0:20:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 這個人現在在幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.90,0:20:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？據說是在作曲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.65,0:20:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.90,0:20:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來比預料中更加沉重呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.48,0:20:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他以前很憧憬你的樂隊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.95,0:20:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差一點就要作為吉他手正式出道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.62,0:20:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.90,0:20:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抬頭望天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.82,0:20:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尋找一座鐵塔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.99,0:21:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想象當自己縱身躍下之時 該有多麼自由
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.34,0:21:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是一場夢麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.13,0:21:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看見自己在一片深紅中追尋遠方的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.90,0:21:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位莫名思憶的伊人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.88,0:21:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎在某人注視下羞澀不安
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.90,0:20:46.02,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Looked up the SKY
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.82,0:20:51.22,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,found a steel tower
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.99,0:21:02.48,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,wondering how I would free if I fall down
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.34,0:21:07.06,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Was it a dream 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.13,0:21:22.43,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I saw deep red chasing for what's far ahead always yearing 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.90,0:21:30.23,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't know why but the beauty I really want 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.88,0:21:38.48,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,may seem to be awkward to someone's eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.05,0:21:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友利一希先生 你認得出我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.72,0:21:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還記得你的妹妹奈央嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.68,0:21:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈..央..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.97,0:21:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 就是奈央
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.38,0:21:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈央..
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.57,0:22:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.16,0:22:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來發生奇跡了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.35,0:22:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是你的歌聲引發的奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.18,0:22:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你是真心的高興呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.26,0:22:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也像你一樣高興哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.02,0:22:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.05,0:22:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.76,0:22:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該說 向前跨進了一步吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.92,0:22:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 可以這麼說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.68,0:22:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天過得很充實 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.36,0:22:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 我明天有打算去你的演唱會
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.01,0:22:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 那麼我會惦記著你這位貴客好好唱的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.59,0:22:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 對你很重要的人也會來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.67,0:22:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也為了那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.38,0:22:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.84,0:22:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然啊 友利 是你改變了我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.00,0:23:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我是乙坂  
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.10,0:23:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是友利
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.78,0:23:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想打聽結果如何了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.26,0:23:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經聽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.05,0:23:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我現在就在醫院外面
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.63,0:23:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擦身而過了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.16,0:23:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 因為護士小姐打電話過來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.23,0:23:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就立刻趕去的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.52,0:23:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他竟然把我認了出來..
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.40,0:23:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的哥哥我好久沒見過了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.68,0:23:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.91,0:23:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 你的判斷太正確了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.79,0:23:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我想跟你道個謝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.45,0:23:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.76,0:23:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.96,0:23:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼明天見了 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.86,0:23:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演唱會 你沒忘吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.73,0:23:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那當然
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.18,0:23:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天是那個人的演唱會麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.07,0:23:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會覺得這麼懷念呢..
